    Annakhil

    The sprawling suburb of Annakhil includes golf courses and palm groves, with paths and horse-carriage tours through 100,000 trees at El Palmeral. Inside that park is Musée de la Palmeraie, showing a century of Moroccan paintings in a 1940s colonial farmhouse. MACAAL is a more modern space, displaying pan-African art. Residential areas have casual tagine restaurants, while resort hotels have chic bars and bistros.
